Player starts in house and can accomplish various tasks, such as:
- getting dressed (by clicking on the closet)
- take out the trash (by clicking on the trashcan)
- clean the kitchen (by clicking on the kitchen table)
- pick up a letter (by clicking on a letter laying on the floor in front of the door)
- leave the house (by clicking on the door):
    - drive to the city (by clicking on the car which teleports you to the next scene)